Top Trending ETL Project Topics (2024–2025)
Perfect for portfolio, resume, interviews, or GitHub projects.

Real-Time ETL with Kafka → Spark Structured Streaming → Delta Lake
Use cases:
Real-time transactions ingestion
Fraud detection
Live dashboards
Highlights:
Kafka consumer ETL
Data cleansing + enrichment
Write to Delta Lake in Bronze → Silver → Gold layers

GenAI Data Pipeline — Chunking, Embeddings & Vector Store ETL (RAG Pipeline)
Stages:
Extract PDFs, docs
Chunk text using PySpark / Scala UDFs
Create embeddings (OpenAI / HuggingFace / AWS Bedrock)
Load into Vector DB (FAISS / Pinecone / Elasticsearch)
Highly demanded project skill today.

ETL for Large-Scale Document Metadata Classification
What you build:
ETL to extract metadata from PDFs
Use Spark NLP (Scala) for:
✔ NER
✔ Regex extraction
✔ Classification
Load curated data into Data Warehouse / Lakehouse

CDC (Change Data Capture) ETL Pipeline — Debezium / Kafka → Spark → Delta
Scenario:
MySQL / Postgres real-time change logs
Transform using Spark
Maintain SCD Type 2 tables in Delta
DevOps + Data Engineering favorite.

IoT ETL Pipeline — MQTT / Kafka → Spark Streaming → Time-Series Store
Use cases:
Energy meters
Vehicle telemetry
Smart home sensors
Tech:
Spark Structured Streaming
TimescaleDB / InfluxDB
Aggregations at 1-sec or 1-min resolution

Retail Sales Analytics ETL with SCD Type 2
Pipeline includes:
Inventory ingestion
Customer dimension
Product dimension
Sales fact
SCD Type 1 and 2 implementation in Scala
Classic project asked in interviews.

Social Media ETL — Twitter/Reddit → Spark → Sentiment + Topic Modeling
Tasks:
Extract comments/posts
Clean & tokenize
Use LDA / embeddings for topic modeling
Load analytics-ready data

Enterprise Log Processing ETL with Spark
Extract logs from:
Nginx
CloudTrail
Application logs
Perform:
Sessionization
Error classification
Outlier detection

Financial ETL — Credit Card Fraud Detection Pipeline
ETL steps:
Ingest transaction data
Apply feature engineering in Spark
Encode categorical values
Write curated data for ML model training

 Healthcare ETL — HL7 / FHIR → Spark → Delta Warehouse
Typical tasks:
Parse HL7 messages
Standardize using FHIR schema
Clean sensitive fields
Produce analytics tables

 Image ETL Pipeline (Spark + MLlib + Cloud Storage)
Steps:
Extract images from Cloud Storage
Resize / normalize / classify
Store results in Delta / PostgreSQL
Works well for:
Defect detection
Medical imaging metadata pipelines

E-commerce Recommendation ETL Pipeline
Includes:
Clickstream ingestion
User-product interactions
Feature creation for ALS model
Curated output for recommendation engine

ETL for GenAI Dataset Preparation
One of the hottest topics now:
Cleaning large textual datasets
Deduplication
Token filtering
Dataset splitting
Preparing training-ready corpora for LLM fine-tuning

